thread.title_full: BRIEF-Sword Group Q3 revenue rises to 33.7 mln euros | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-Sword Group Q3 revenue rises to 33.7 mln euros
text:
Oct 22 Sword Group SE :
* Reports Q3 consolidated revenue of 33.7 million euros ($37.60 million) compared to 28.3 million euros a year ago
* Q3 consolidated EBITDA is 5.2 million euros compared to 4.9 million euros a year ago
* Says it will deliver results that exceed forecasts
* Plans double digit organic growth for 2016 Source text for Eikon:
